Description: GnomacTerminal - customized terminal emulator
 GnomacTerminal is a fork of GNOME Terminal with a custom bundled VTE
 library. It provides a complete terminal emulator that can coexist
 with the system gnome-terminal installation. Designed as a platform
 for customizing modifier key behavior for better macOS-style
 keyboard emulation.
